        <Paragraph>
             This sample showcases the Customized Databound Template capability of GridDataControl. The GridDataControl supports applying templates to the individual columns. GridDataVisibleColumn contains two property CellItemTemplate and CellEditItemTemplate. CellItemTemplate property is used to set DataTemplate for loading the visible column. CellEditItemTemplate property is used to set DataTemplate for editing.
